\phi_{j}=\frac{2\pi}{\lambda}\left(\boldsymbol{S}_{0}-\boldsymbol{S}\right)\cdot\boldsymbol{R}=\frac{2\pi}{\lambda}\left(\boldsymbol{S}_{0}-\boldsymbol{S}\right)\cdot\left[x_{j}\boldsymbol{a}+y_{j}\boldsymbol{b}+z_{j}\boldsymbol{c}\right]
\]

\end_inset

利用(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-14"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 上式变为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\phi_{j}=2\pi\left(hx_{j}+ky_{j}+lz_{j}\right)\label{eq:9-34}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

把上式代入到(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-33"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 并把
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

个原子的散射波迭加起来, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\sum_{j=1}^{q}E_{j}=E_{0}\left[\sum_{j=1}^{q}f_{j}e^{i2\pi\left(hx_{j}+ky_{j}+lz_{j}\right)}\right]e^{i2\pi\left(t/T-x/\lambda\right)}\label{eq:9-35}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

按照结构因子的定义,  
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

个原子散射波的振幅与一个电子散射波振幅之比即为
\begin_inset Formula $F_{hkl}$
\end_inset

。比较上式和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-25"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 得结构因子为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
F_{hkl}=\sum_{j=1}^{q}f_{j}e^{i2\pi\left(hx_{j}+ky_{j}+lz_{j}\right)}\label{eq:9-36}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

把上式代入到(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-31"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 可得原胞在衍射方向
\begin_inset Formula $(hkl)$
\end_inset

所散射的 X 射线强度: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
I=I_{e}F_{hkl}F_{hkl}^{*}=I_{e}\left[\sum_{j=1}^{q}f_{j}\cos2\pi\left(hx_{j}+ky_{j}+lz_{j}\right)\right]^{2}+I_{e}\left[\sum_{j=1}^{q}f_{j}\sin2\pi\left(hx_{j}+ky_{j}+lz_{j}\right)\right]^{2}\label{eq:9-37}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

因此, 如果已知原子散射因子
\begin_inset Formula $f_{j}$
\end_inset

, 就可由衍射强度
\begin_inset Formula $I$
\end_inset

推算出原庖中原子的分数坐标, 反之, 如果已知原胞中原子的坐标, 容易算出衍射线的强、弱和消失的规律。衍射线消失, 即衍射线的强度为零, 称为消光。下面讨论几种
结构类型的消光规律。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
1) 体心结构
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
体心结构的原胞含有两个相同的原子, 其分数坐标为
\begin_inset Formula $(0,0,0)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2}\right)$
\end_inset

。将分数坐标代入到(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-37"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
I=I_{e}f^{2}\left[1+\cos\left(h+k+l\right)\pi\right]^{2}+I_{e}f^{2}\left[1+\sin\left(h+k+l\right)\pi\right]^{2}
\]

\end_inset

因衍射指标为整数, 故第二项为零, 若
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
h+k+l=\text{偶数}
\]

\end_inset

则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
I=4f^{2}I
\]

\end_inset

若
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
h+k+l=\text{奇数}
\]

\end_inset

则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
I=0
\]

\end_inset

计算结果表明, 并不是满足Laue方程的
\begin_inset Formula $hkl$
\end_inset

级衍射都能发生,  在体心结构中, 不会出现
\begin_inset Formula $h+k+l$
\end_inset

等于奇数的衍射线, 如100, 111, 120等级次的衍射不能出现, 这就是体心结构消光规律。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
2) 面心结构
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
面心结构的原胞中含有四个原子, 其分数坐标为
\begin_inset Formula $(0,0,0)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2},0\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(0,\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\frac{1}{2},0,\frac{1}{2}\right)$
\end_inset

, 将其代入到公式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-37"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 中, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
I=I_{e}f^{2}\left[1+\cos\left(h+k\right)\pi+\cos\left(k+l\right)\pi+\cos\left(h+l\right)\pi\right]^{2}
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $hkl$
\end_inset

全为偶数或全为奇数时, 衍射线最强: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
I=16f^{2}I_{e}
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $hkl$
\end_inset

部分为偶数, 部分为奇数时, 则产生消光而得不到衍射线。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
3) 简单结构
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
简单结构的原胞只含有一个原子, 坐标为
\begin_inset Formula $(0,0,0)$
\end_inset

, 利用(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-37"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
I=f^{2}I
\]

\end_inset

即简单结构不产生消光, 凡满足Laue方程的衍射线都能产生。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
4) 金刚石结构
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
金刚石的原胞包含八个原子, 其分数坐标为
\begin_inset Formula $(0,0,0)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2},0\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(0,\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\frac{1}{2},0,\frac{1}{2}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
