\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\frac{3}{4},\frac{1}{4},\frac{3}{4}\right)$
\end_inset

。将这些坐标代入到 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-37"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
I=I_{e}f^{2}\left[1+\cos\left(h+k\right)\pi+\cos\left(k+l\right)\pi+\cos\left(h+l\right)\pi\right]^{2}\cdot2\left[1+\cos\frac{\pi}{2}\left(h+k+l\right)\right]
\]

\end_inset

上式表明, 当
\begin_inset Formula $h$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

, 奇偶混杂时会产生消光, 这与一般的面心结构的消光规律相同, 而且, 当
