\begin_layout Subsection
电子密度
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

与结构因子
\begin_inset Formula $F_{hkl}$
\end_inset

关系的推导
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
作为本节的结尾, 我们将导出电子密度
\begin_inset Formula $\rho(x,y,z)$
\end_inset

与结构因子
\begin_inset Formula $F_{hkl}$
\end_inset

的关系。电子密度
\begin_inset Formula $\rho(x,y,z)$
\end_inset

常表示为空间坐标
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

的函数, 为此先把分数坐标化为空间坐标。因分数坐标分别以 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{b}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{c}$
\end_inset

的长度为单位, 所以分数坐标
\begin_inset Formula $x_{j}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{j}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $z_{j}$
\end_inset

与空间坐标
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

的关系为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
x_{j}=\frac{x}{a},y_{j}=\frac{y}{b},z_{j}=\frac{z}{c}\label{eq:9-38}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设晶胞中一点
\begin_inset Formula $P(x,y,z)$
\end_inset

的位矢为
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{r}$
\end_inset

, 则晶胞中所有电子的散射波为 
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

点
\begin_inset Formula $\rho(\boldsymbol{r})dv$
\end_inset

个电子散射波的迭加并对整个晶胞体积积分。仿照 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-28"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 可得到晶胞内所有电子所产生的散射波为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
E=E_{0}e^{i2\pi\left(t/T-x/\lambda\right)}\int_{0}^{a}\int_{0}^{b}\int_{0}^{c}\rho(\boldsymbol{r})e^{i\frac{2\pi}{\lambda}\left(\boldsymbol{S}_{0}-\boldsymbol{S}\right)\cdot\boldsymbol{r}}dv\label{eq:9-39}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

按照结构因子的定义, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
F_{hkl}=\int_{0}^{a}\int_{0}^{b}\int_{0}^{c}\rho(\boldsymbol{r})e^{i\frac{2\pi}{\lambda}\left(\boldsymbol{S}_{0}-\boldsymbol{S}\right)\cdot\boldsymbol{r}}dv\label{eq:9-40}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

式中的位相差仍可由 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-34"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式表示, 只是应把分数坐标换成空间坐标, 即
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\phi=\frac{2\pi}{\lambda}\left(\boldsymbol{S}_{0}-\boldsymbol{S}\right)\cdot\boldsymbol{r}=2\pi\left(\frac{hx}{a}+\frac{ky}{b}+\frac{lz}{c}\right)\label{eq:9-41}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

把上式代入到 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-40"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 得结构因子为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
F_{hkl}=\int_{0}^{a}\int_{0}^{b}\int_{0}^{c}\rho(x,y,z)e^{2\pi i(hx/z+ky/b+lz/c)}dxdydz\label{eq:9-42}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

因为电子密度
\begin_inset Formula $\rho(x,y,z)$
\end_inset

是晶格周期性的函数, 所以可将其展开成三维的 Fourier 级数
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\rho(x,y,z)=\sum_{p}\sum_{q}\sum_{r}A(pqr)e^{2\pi i(hx/z+ky/b+lz/c)}\label{eq:9-43}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

为了得到 Fourier 系数
\begin_inset Formula $A(pqr)$
\end_inset

, 将上式代入到 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:9-42"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式中, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
F_{hkl}=\int_{0}^{a}\int_{0}^{b}\int_{0}^{c}\sum_{p}\sum_{q}\sum_{r}A(pqr)e^{2\pi i(hx/z+ky/b+lz/c)}dxdydz\label{eq:9-44}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

因为指数函数遍及一个完全周期的积分总是等于零, 故上式求和中只剩一项不为零, 即对应于
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
p=-h,q=-k,r=-l\label{eq:9-45}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

的项不为零,  于是有
