\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\pm1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\pm2$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\cdots$
\end_inset

的各层线上的分立衍射点所组成。把用圆筒形底片摄取的衍射图展开后, 即如图9.50右图所示。其中
\begin_inset Formula $l=0$
\end_inset

为中央层线, 
\begin_inset Formula $l=\pm1$
\end_inset

为第一层线, 
\begin_inset Formula $l=\pm2$
\end_inset

为第二层线, 以此类推。设感光胶片圆筒的半径为
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{l}$
\end_inset

为第
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

层线与中央层线的距离, 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

为衍射方向与
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{c}$
\end_inset

的夹角, 则
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\cos\gamma=H_{l}/\sqrt{R^{2}+H_{l}^{2}}\label{eq:9-49}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

